<h1>About This Project</h1>
<br>
<p>
  This project is a Comic Collection app where users can browse, search, and add reviews for their favorite comics. 
  The system allows users to create new comics, associate them with a publisher and series, and leave ratings and reviews.
</p>
<br>

<h2>Project Overview</h2>
<p>
  The Comic Collection app was built using Ruby on Rails with a relational database that includes entities such as:
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Users</strong>: Can add comics, write reviews, and search for comics.</li>
    <li><strong>Comics</strong>: Contains title, description, publisher, and series. Users can add new comics and write reviews.</li>
    <li><strong>Publishers</strong>: Comics are associated with publishers.</li>
    <li><strong>Series</strong>: Comics are grouped by series.</li>
    <li><strong>Reviews</strong>: Users can leave reviews for comics.</li>
  </ul>
</p>
<br>
