<h3>Explanation of Relationships<h3>
<p>One-to-Many Relationships:<br>
A User has many Comics and many Reviews.<br>
A Publisher has many Series and many Comics.<br>
A Series has many Comics.<br>
A Comic has many Reviews.<br>
Many-to-One Relationships:<br>
A Comic belongs to one User, one Publisher, and one Series.<br>
A Review belongs to one User and one Comic.<br>
A Series belongs to one Publisher.<br>


